# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables.
# IMPORTANT: in the Vercel UI, paste each VALUE WITHOUT surrounding quotes and
# with no leading/trailing spaces. (Quotes are only needed in a local .env file.)
# Replace PWD with your Supabase DB password, URL-encoded:  +  ->  %2B   !  ->  %21
# Host/region (aws-1-ap-southeast-2) and project ref are pre-filled.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# DATABASE_URL  → Supabase TRANSACTION pooler (port 6543) — app runtime
postgresql://postgres.uxubotypikmjxzascwjo:PWD@aws-1-ap-southeast-2.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres?pgbouncer=true&connection_limit=1

# DIRECT_URL    → Supabase SESSION pooler (port 5432) — migrations/seed
postgresql://postgres.uxubotypikmjxzascwjo:PWD@aws-1-ap-southeast-2.pooler.supabase.com:5432/postgres

# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY  → your Anthropic key (leave blank for offline AI mode)
# SPM_AI_MODEL       → claude-sonnet-4-6
